# 💰 Expense Tracker

A full-stack web application to track daily expenses with user authentication, category filtering, and monthly summaries.

## 🚀 Features

- User Registration & Login
- Add, View, and Delete Expenses
- Category-wise filtering (Food, Travel, Shopping, Education)
- Monthly expense summary
- Responsive and clean UI

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Storage:** localStorage (Browser)
- **Tools:** Git, GitHub, VS Code

